@startuml payment-state
title Payment & Transaction State Diagram

[*] --> PENDING_PAYMENT : Auction winner\ndetermined\n/ payment email sent

PENDING_PAYMENT --> PAYMENT_PROCESSING : Buyer initiates\npayment via gateway

PAYMENT_PROCESSING --> PAYMENT_FAILED : Gateway returns\nfailure / timeout

PAYMENT_FAILED --> PAYMENT_PROCESSING : Buyer retries\npayment

PAYMENT_FAILED --> CANCELLED : Max retries\nexceeded or\nbuyer abandons

PAYMENT_PROCESSING --> IN_ESCROW : Gateway confirms\npayment success\n/ funds held

IN_ESCROW --> SHIPPED : Seller marks\nitem as shipped\n+ tracking info

SHIPPED --> DELIVERY_CONFIRMED : Buyer clicks\n"Confirm Delivery"\nwithin 7 days

SHIPPED --> DELIVERY_CONFIRMED : 7-day window\nexpires\n(auto-confirm)

DELIVERY_CONFIRMED --> COMPLETED : Funds released\nto seller\n/ receipt generated

IN_ESCROW --> DISPUTED : Buyer raises\ndispute before\ndelivery confirmed

SHIPPED --> DISPUTED : Buyer raises\ndispute (item\nnot received /\nnot as described)

DISPUTED --> REFUNDED : Admin rules\nin buyer's favour\n/ partial or\nfull refund issued

DISPUTED --> COMPLETED : Admin rules\nin seller's favour\n/ funds released

REFUNDED --> [*] : Refund processed,\nrecord archived

COMPLETED --> [*] : Transaction closed,\nparties prompted\nto leave reviews

CANCELLED --> [*] : Transaction\narchived

note right of IN_ESCROW
  Funds held by platform.
  Neither buyer nor seller
  can access until state
  transitions out of escrow.
end note

note right of DISPUTED
  Escrow release frozen.
  Admin arbitrates with
  evidence from both parties.
end note

@enduml
